summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting deeds for certain real property in Section 22, Township 22 North, Range 4 East, W.M., Yorkshire, Cherry Park Estates, Division A, Parkside Division No. 2 and Burkeland's First Addition, all as contemplated by Ordinance 112727; authorizing the sale thereof as recommended by the Midway Coordinating Committee; authorizing the Mayor to sign Statutory Warranty Deeds and disbursing funds received to the Solid Waste Fund.
